description.displayText: I interviewed Danielle for a full-time nanny position for my 2 year old and 5 month old.  We ended up going with a different candidate but it was an EXTREMELY hard decision.  We were really impressed with Danielle's maturity, attention to detail, thoughtfulness, and obvious care for young children.  Any family that ends up with Danielle will be very lucky!
